        "content": "<p>cc <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"413824\">@Gary Guo</span> </p>\n<p>Apparently, when a build_assert!() fails, it simply prints this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;..</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">more</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">unrelated</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">stuff</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">..</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">UPD</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"n\">include</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">generated</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">utsversion</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">h</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">CC</span><span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">init</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">version</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">timestamp</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">KSYMS</span><span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tmp_vmlinux0</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">kallsyms</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">S</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">AS</span><span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tmp_vmlinux0</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">kallsyms</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">LD</span><span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">tmp_vmlinux1</span>\n<span class=\"n\">ld</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">lld</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">error</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">undefined</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">symbol</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">rust_build_error</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;-------------------</span>\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">referenced</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">usercopy_64</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">c</span>\n<span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\">               </span><span class=\"n\">vmlinux</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">o</span><span class=\"p\">:(</span><span class=\"n\">panthor_gpu_init_info</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span><span class=\"p\">]:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">***</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">Makefile</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">vmlinux</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">34</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">vmlinux</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n<span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">]:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">***</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">home</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dwls</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">dev</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">Makefile</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">1156</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">vmlinux</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n<span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">***</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Makefile</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">224</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">__sub</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Is this expected? I see this <code>assertion failed</code> string is not being printed at all, apparently:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#[macro_export]</span>\n<span class=\"fm\">macro_rules!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">build_assert</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"cp\">$cond</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">expr</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$(,</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"o\">?</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"cp\">$cond</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"cp\">$crate</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">build_error</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"fm\">concat!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"assertion failed: \"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"fm\">stringify!</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"cp\">$cond</span><span class=\"p\">)));</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}};</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"cp\">$cond</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">expr</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cp\">$msg</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"nc\">expr</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"cp\">$cond</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"cp\">$crate</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">build_error</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"cp\">$msg</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}};</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
